        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Federal Law Enforcement Service Weapon Purchase Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill generally permits a federal law enforcement officer to purchase a retired handgun from the agency that issued a handgun to the officer.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The bill directs the General Services Administration to develop policies to facilitate the sale and disposition of eligible handguns.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
